#. Flow Chart Best Code Editor.
  1. https://mermaid.live/
  2. https://app.diagrams.net/?src=about      (draw.io)
  3. ppt

AI use in create mermaid code Query chatgpt and deepseek.

example:
ChatGPT
i want to make a flow diagram of smart streetlight wihch is intigrated with iccc. write a code to make flow diagram in mermid.live

graph TD;
    A[Smart Streetlight System] -->|Collects Sensor Data| B[Light Sensors & Motion Detectors];
    A -->|Receives Commands| C[ICCC (Integrated Command & Control Center)];
    
    B -->|Sends Data| D[Streetlight Controller];
    C -->|Sends Control Signals| D;
    
    D -->|Adjusts Brightness| E[Streetlight];
    D -->|Sends Status Updates| C;
    
    E -->|Power Optimization| F[Energy Management System];
    F -->|Reports Power Consumption| C;
    
    C -->|Monitors & Analyzes Data| G[Data Analytics & Dashboard];
    G -->|Generates Alerts & Reports| H[Operators & Maintenance Team];
    
    H -->|Performs Maintenance| I[Field Technicians];

Deepseek
i want to make a flow diagram of smart streetlight wihch is intigrated with iccc. write a code to make flow diagram in mermid.live

flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Streetlight Status]
    B --> C{Is Nighttime?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Turn ON Light]
    C -- No --> E[Turn OFF Light]
    D --> F{Object Detected?}
    E --> Z[Send Status to ICC]
    F -- Yes --> G[Increase Brightness]
    F -- No --> H[Maintain Normal Brightness]
    G --> I[Send Alert to ICC]
    H --> Z
    I --> Z
    Z --> K[Receive Commands from ICC]
    K --> L{Adjust Settings?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Update Parameters]
    L -- No --> N[Continue Operation]
    M --> B
    N --> B
    
    style A fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#388E3C
    style B fill:#2196F3,stroke:#0b7dda
    style C fill:#FF9800,stroke:#e68a00
    style D fill:#8BC34A,stroke:#7CB342
    style E fill:#F44336,stroke:#D32F2F
    style F fill:#FF9800,stroke:#e68a00
    style G fill:#8BC34A,stroke:#7CB342
    style H fill:#8BC34A,stroke:#7CB342
    style I fill:#FFEB3B,stroke:#FBC02D
    style Z fill:#9C27B0,stroke:#7B1FA2
    style K fill:#607D8B,stroke:#455A64
    style L fill:#FF9800,stroke:#e68a00
    style M fill:#8BC34A,stroke:#7CB342
    style N fill:#8BC34A,stroke:#7CB342
